edu.ucla.sspace.graph

Class SparseDirectedTypedEdgeSet<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractSet<DirectedTypedEdge<T>>
        • edu.ucla.sspace.graph.SparseDirectedTypedEdgeSet<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EdgeSet<DirectedTypedEdge<T>>, Serializable, Iterable<DirectedTypedEdge<T>>, Collection<DirectedTypedEdge<T>>, Set<DirectedTypedEdge<T>>

    public class SparseDirectedTypedEdgeSet<T>
extends AbstractSet<DirectedTypedEdge<T>>
implements EdgeSet<DirectedTypedEdge<T>>, Serializable
    An EdgeSet implementation that stores DirectedTypedEdge instances for a vertex. This class provides additional methods beyond the EdgeSet interface for interacting with edges on the basis of their type and their orientation.
    See Also:
